<plot>The short film Canoe tells a story about how man fights with its inside demons. The film takes basis in a young woman, we see her and her journey inside herself. The film is told in a surreal way, no dialog, only pictures and sound and music. Eventhough the film is surreal, the three parts structure is clear; beginning, middle part, ending, turning points, so it is rather an fiction film than an art film. The film is very unique and compelling for the audience</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?093062</url></doc>
